SUBCONTRACTOR AGREEMENT
This Agreement made on: 1 July 2024
BETWEEN:
ABC Construction Pty Ltd (ABN: 12 345 678 901)
123 Builder Street, Sydney NSW 2000
(hereinafter 'the Principal')
AND:
Bright Spark Electrical Pty Ltd (ABN: 44 223 445 667)
321 Sparky Lane, Auburn NSW 2144
Electrical Contractor License: EL-123456
(hereinafter 'the Subcontractor')
1. SCOPE OF WORKS
The Subcontractor agrees to supply, install and complete all electrical works for:
Project: New Two-Storey Dwelling - 123 Sunset Boulevard, Sydney NSW 2000
Including but not limited to:
(cid:127) Complete electrical installation as per approved plans dated 15/01/2024
(cid:127) Main switchboard, distribution boards, circuit protection
(cid:127) Power and lighting circuits, power points, switches, light fittings
(cid:127) Hardwired smoke alarms (interconnected)
(cid:127) Hot water, oven/cooktop circuits
(cid:127) Testing and certification as per AS/NZS 3000
2. CONTRACT PRICE
Total Contract Sum: $28,540.00 (including GST)
Paymen
